xul-ext-classic-theme-restorer (1.5.7~beta2-1nano) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release
    1.5.7~beta1
      locale(s)]
        - Slovenian (sl-SI) translation updated (thanks to Klofutar)
        - Estonian (et) translation updated (thanks to Maidur)
        - Portuguese (pt-BR) translation updated (thanks to igorruckert)
      fix(es)]
        - Fx51+: General UI (1) > bookmarks menu button > popups panel menu appearance
        - Linux: 'General UI (3) > inverted icon settings' (needs more testing)
      new option(s)]
        - Fx48+: Tabs (1) > switch for 'browser.ctrlTab.previews' preference
        - Tabs colors&text > unloaded/unread tabs > 'reduce tab visibility'
        - Firefox button > button on toolbar > more icons
        - MacOS: General UI (1) > 'movable back/forward buttons' > reduce nav-bar height
        - Fx51+: General UI (2) > switch for 'browser.download.showPanelDropmarker' preferences
        - Add-on manager > Always show 'Recent updates' category
        - Toolbar (2) > Findbar > Close findbar when scrolling page
      general change(s)]
        - Windows/Linux: rewritten 'General UI (1) > movable back/forward buttons > reduce nav-bar height
        - Code tweaks for 'General UI (3) > inverted icon settings' 
    1.5.7~beta2
      locale(s)]
        - Chinese (zh-CN) translation updated (thanks to Cye3s)
        - Russian (ru) translation updated (thanks to Alexei)
        - Slovenian (sl-SI) translation updated (thanks to Klofutar)
        - Polish (pl-PL) translation updated (thanks to Mrere)
      fix(es)]
        - dropmarkers & 'General UI (1) > movable b/f buttons > reduce nav-bar height' option 

