    1.4.3beta~12
      [new options > General UI (1)] 'about:preferences window appearance' v1&v2 for tabs
        Note: General > Homepage > 'Use Current page' will always add 'about:preferences'
        as homepage, because thats the only page currently opened in the new window. No
        difference to browsers default preferences ui with only preferences tab open.
