      [new] option: hide double arrow on nav-bars end (experimental chevron fix)
      [change] prefwindow: last selected category gets 'remembered'
      [change] Windows + squared tabs: increased space between tabs and window controls
    1.2.5~beta13
      [locale] Polish (pl-PL) translation updated (Mrere)
      [locale] Ukrainian (uk) translation updated (thanks to Sacredwheels)
      [change] bookmarks star & rss feed buttons in urlbar
      [change] remove obsolete code
    1.2.5~beta14
      [new] options to enable two more additional toolbars
      [change] cleanup 'appmenu->web developer' popup
    1.2.5~beta15
      [locale] Polish (pl-PL) translation updated (thanks to Mrere)
      [locale] Ukrainian (uk) translation updated (thanks to Sacredwheels)
      [fix] additional toolbars (& some complete themes): toolbars were always visible

